column11: The data you carry is vital to the remaining Federation fleet. You'll need supplies for the journey, so make sure to explore each sector before moving on to the next. But get to the exit before the pursuing Rebel fleet can catch up!  TIP: Sound -  Go into the options menu to turn on or off the sound effects and music.
The station was apparently designed to outfit Rebel ships with Drone Systems. You find a functioning Schematic.
The scout jumps away. They are sure to have informed the fleet of your position. You must get to the next Sector as soon as possible!
